HEADWORD: grantee
<hw>gran*tee"</hw> <pr>(gr⟦adot⟧n*t⟦emac⟧")</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Law)</fld> <def>The person to whom a grant or conveyance is
made.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His grace will not survive the poor <qex>grantee</qex> he
